text.tspan: You are your Harrier - welcome to the battlefield. Attack other factions, or defend
your own base. Support your soldiers by giving orders and deploying special attacks
during battle to support them.
Build your outpost, and maintain your defenses system against attackers
by deploying and upgrading your base. The gameplay will go on even when you are
away, and the defense results will be rewarded according to the outcome of events
during this time.
Upgrade and specialize your army to fight against others. Win the fight
and plunder your enemy base. Send your Harriers by recruiting new people to your
troops.
The game features asynchronous multiplayer combat where attackers compete
against other players' defensive bases. Watch replays of your opponent's attacks and
perform successful reprisals to earn bonus loot and resources.
The game contains a system to test your guts. If you would like to have more
benefits, you gotta be ready to put your resources on the line. The more you bet, the
bigger the win.
Play against holders of other projects together with your
friends and earn tokens. Reach the top of the leaderboards. Holders of DUST80 will
enjoy the best interactive gameplay experience.
